<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Arjun Mehta — Full Stack Developer</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --ac:#00D9FF;
  --ac10:rgba(0,217,255,0.10);
  --ac20:rgba(0,217,255,0.18);
  --ac30:rgba(0,217,255,0.30);
  --bg:#07080A;
  --bg2:#0C0D10;
  --bg3:#111318;
  --text:#F0EDE6;
  --muted:rgba(240,237,230,0.55);
  --faint:rgba(240,237,230,0.28);
  --border:rgba(240,237,230,0.07);
  --border2:rgba(240,237,230,0.14);
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{
  background:var(--bg);
  background-image:radial-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size:32px 32px;
  color:var(--text);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* LOADER */
#loader{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:99999;background:var(--bg);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:32px;transition:opacity .6s,visibility .6s}
#loader.done{opacity:0;visibility:hidden}
.loader-terminal{width:340px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden}
.loader-topbar{background:var(--bg3);padding:10px 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.loader-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%}
.loader-dot:nth-child(1){background:#FF5F57}
.loader-dot:nth-child(2){background:#FEBC2E}
.loader-dot:nth-child(3){background:#28C840}
.loader-body{padding:20px 20px 24px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:1.8}
.loader-line{color:var(--muted);min-height:1.8em}
.loader-line .prefix{color:var(--ac)}
.loader-line .typed{color:var(--text)}
.blink-cur{display:inline-block;width:7px;height:13px;background:var(--ac);vertical-align:middle;animation:blink 1s step-end infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}
.loader-bar-wrap{width:340px;height:1px;background:var(--border);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.loader-bar{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:0%;background:var(--ac);transition:width .05s linear}

/* PROGRESS */
#progress{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:1px;width:0%;background:var(--ac);z-index:9000;pointer-events:none;box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--ac)}

/* NAV */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:900;padding:28px 56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;transition:all .4s}
nav.scrolled{background:rgba(7,8,10,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);padding:18px 56px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-logo{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:16px;color:var(--ac);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:.04em}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--faint)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:36px}
.nav-links a{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;transition:color .2s;position:relative}
.nav-links a::before{content:'> ';color:var(--ac);opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}.nav-links a:hover::before{opacity:1}
.nav-cta{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:10px 20px;border:1px solid var(--ac);border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ac);transition:all .2s;background:var(--ac10)}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--ac20)}

/* HERO */
#hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:120px 48px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
#hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 50% 50%,rgba(0,217,255,.04) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
/* Scanlines */
#hero::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(0,217,255,.015) 2px,rgba(0,217,255,.015) 4px);pointer-events:none}

.hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:800px}
.hero-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ac);margin-bottom:40px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .5s .2s}
.hero-label.go{opacity:1}
.hero-label::before{content:'[';color:var(--faint)}.hero-label::after{content:']';color:var(--faint)}

.hero-tagline{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(32px,4.5vw,64px);letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:8px;min-height:3em}
.hero-tagline .typed-text{color:var(--text)}
.hero-tagline .ac{color:var(--ac)}
.blink{display:inline-block;width:3px;height:.9em;background:var(--ac);vertical-align:middle;animation:blink 1s step-end infinite;margin-left:2px}

.hero-sub{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;font-weight:300;max-width:480px;margin:28px auto 44px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px);transition:opacity .7s,transform .7s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)}
.hero-sub.go{opacity:1;transform:none}
.hero-btns{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:20px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px);transition:opacity .7s,transform .7s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)}
.hero-btns.go{opacity:1;transform:none}
.btn-p{background:transparent;color:var(--ac);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:14px 32px;border:1px solid var(--ac);border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;transition:all .2s;display:inline-block;background:var(--ac10)}
.btn-p:hover{background:var(--ac20);box-shadow:0 0 20px var(--ac10)}
.btn-s{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;transition:color .2s}
.btn-s:hover{color:var(--text)}

.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:36px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:10px;opacity:0;animation:fadeIn 1s 3s forwards}
@keyframes fadeIn{to{opacity:.35}}
.scroll-hint span{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint)}
.scroll-line{width:1px;height:44px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,var(--ac),transparent);animation:sa 1.6s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes sa{0%{transform:scaleY(0);transform-origin:top}50%{transform:scaleY(1);transform-origin:top}50.1%{transform-origin:bottom}100%{transform:scaleY(0);transform-origin:bottom}}

/* LAYOUT */
.wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 56px}
section{padding:120px 0}
.section-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ac);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.section-label::before{content:'//';color:var(--ac);font-size:13px}
h2{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,48px);letter-spacing:-.02em;color:var(--text);line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:56px}
h2 em{font-style:normal;color:var(--ac)}

/* STATS */
#stats{padding:0 0 100px}
.stats-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg2)}
.stat-col{padding:44px 40px;border-right:1px solid var(--border)}
.stat-col:last-child{border-right:none}
.stat-n{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(40px,4vw,58px);color:var(--ac);letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;display:block;text-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(0,217,255,.3)}
.stat-l{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px;display:block;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.04em}

/* ABOUT */
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center}
.about-visual{aspect-ratio:4/5;border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:24px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.about-visual-grid{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:radial-gradient(var(--border2) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px}
.about-visual-glow{position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 30%,rgba(0,217,255,.06) 0%,transparent 70%)}
.code-block{position:relative;z-index:2;background:rgba(7,8,10,.9);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:4px;padding:16px;font-size:12px;line-height:1.9}
.code-block .kw{color:var(--ac)}.code-block .str{color:#98D8C8}.code-block .num{color:#FFB347}.code-block .cm{color:var(--faint)}
.about-copy p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;font-weight:300}
.about-copy p+p{margin-top:18px}
.tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:28px}
.tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.04em;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:3px;border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--faint);transition:all .2s}
.tag:hover{border-color:var(--ac30);color:var(--ac);background:var(--ac10)}

/* SERVICES — terminal style */
.svc-list{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.svc-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:30px 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:100px 1fr 120px;align-items:start;gap:24px;transition:background .2s;padding-left:16px;margin-left:-16px;padding-right:16px;border-radius:4px}
.svc-item:hover{background:var(--bg2)}
.svc-n{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--ac);padding-top:4px;font-weight:500}
.svc-title{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(16px,1.8vw,20px);color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-.01em}
.svc-desc{margin-top:8px;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;max-width:480px}
.svc-tag{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ac);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;text-align:right;padding-top:5px;opacity:.7}

/* PROCESS */
.process-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden}
.p-step{background:var(--bg2);padding:40px;transition:background .25s}
.p-step:hover{background:var(--bg3)}
.p-num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--ac);letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:16px}
.p-name{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:18px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:12px}
.p-desc{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7}

/* TESTIMONIALS */
.testi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px}
.testi-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:32px 28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;transition:border-color .25s,transform .3s}
.testi-card:hover{border-color:var(--ac30);transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,217,255,.05)}
.tq{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:40px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ac);line-height:1;opacity:.6}
.testi-text{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;font-weight:300;flex:1}
.testi-author{padding-top:20px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.t-name{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--text)}
.t-role{font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:4px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}

/* FAQ */
.faq-list{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.faq-q{width:100%;padding:26px 0;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;text-align:left}
.faq-q-t{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:500;font-size:15px;color:var(--text)}
.faq-q-t::before{content:'> ';color:var(--ac)}
.faq-ic{flex-shrink:0;width:26px;height:26px;border:1px solid var(--border2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;transition:all .3s}
.faq-item.open .faq-ic{border-color:var(--ac);color:var(--ac);transform:rotate(45deg)}
.faq-a{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .45s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)}
.faq-a-in{padding:0 0 26px;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;max-width:640px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}

/* CTA */
.cta-box{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:88px 80px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.cta-box::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 110%,rgba(0,217,255,.08) 0%,transparent 65%);pointer-events:none}
.cta-box::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(0,217,255,.01) 2px,rgba(0,217,255,.01) 4px);pointer-events:none}
.cta-box h2{margin-bottom:16px}
.cta-box p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);max-width:400px;margin:0 auto 40px;line-height:1.75;font-weight:300}
.btn-cta{background:var(--ac10);color:var(--ac);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:18px 52px;border:1px solid var(--ac);border-radius:3px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;transition:all .2s;position:relative}
.btn-cta:hover{background:var(--ac20);box-shadow:0 0 32px rgba(0,217,255,.15);transform:translateY(-2px)}

/* FOOTER */
footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:28px 56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.f-name{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--faint)}
.f-copy{font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:.04em;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}

/* REVEAL */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity .7s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1),transform .7s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1)}
.reveal.vis{opacity:1;transform:none}
.d1{transition-delay:.1s}.d2{transition-delay:.2s}.d3{transition-delay:.3s}

@media(max-width:900px){
  nav{padding:20px 24px}nav.scrolled{padding:14px 24px}.nav-links{display:none}
  #hero{padding:120px 24px 80px}.wrap{padding:0 24px}section{padding:80px 0}
  .about-grid,.testi-grid,.process-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .about-visual{display:none}.stats-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .stat-col{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
  .svc-item{grid-template-columns:80px 1fr}.svc-tag{display:none}
  footer{padding:24px}.cta-box{padding:48px 24px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="loader">
  <div class="loader-terminal">
    <div class="loader-topbar">
      <div class="loader-dot"></div><div class="loader-dot"></div><div class="loader-dot"></div>
      <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--faint);margin-left:8px">portfolio.sh</span>
    </div>
    <div class="loader-body">
      <div class="loader-line" id="ll1"><span class="prefix">$ </span><span class="typed" id="lt1"></span><span class="blink-cur" id="lc1"></span></div>
      <div class="loader-line" id="ll2" style="opacity:0"><span class="prefix">→ </span><span class="typed" id="lt2"></span><span class="blink-cur" id="lc2" style="display:none"></span></div>
      <div class="loader-line" id="ll3" style="opacity:0"><span class="prefix">✓ </span><span class="typed" id="lt3" style="color:var(--ac)"></span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="loader-bar-wrap"><div class="loader-bar" id="loaderBar"></div></div>
</div>

<div id="progress"></div>

<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo"><span>~/</span>arjun-mehta</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#about">about</a><a href="#services">services</a>
    <a href="#process">process</a><a href="#testimonials">results</a>
  </div>
  <a href="#cta" class="nav-cta">./hire-me</a>
</nav>

<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-label go" id="heroLabel">Full Stack Developer</div>
    <div class="hero-tagline">
      <div id="typedLine"></div>
      <span class="blink" id="heroCursor"></span>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-sub" id="heroSub">Building scalable systems and clean interfaces that solve real problems — shipped on time, built to last.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns" id="heroBtns">
      <a href="#services" class="btn-p">./view-services</a>
      <a href="#testimonials" class="btn-s">see results →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint"><span>scroll</span><div class="scroll-line"></div></div>
</section>

<div id="stats" class="wrap">
  <div class="stats-row reveal">
    <div class="stat-col"><span class="stat-n" data-target="94" data-suffix="+">0+</span><span class="stat-l">// projects_shipped</span></div>
    <div class="stat-col"><span class="stat-n" data-target="100" data-suffix="%">0%</span><span class="stat-l">// on_time_delivery</span></div>
    <div class="stat-col"><span class="stat-n" data-target="5" data-suffix=" yrs">0 yrs</span><span class="stat-l">// years_experience</span></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section id="about">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-visual reveal">
        <div class="about-visual-grid"></div>
        <div class="about-visual-glow"></div>
        <div class="code-block">
          <div><span class="kw">const</span> arjun = {</div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;role: <span class="str">"Full Stack Dev"</span>,</div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;stack: [<span class="str">"React"</span>, <span class="str">"Node"</span>, <span class="str">"Go"</span>],</div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;clients: <span class="num">47</span>,</div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;onTime: <span class="num">true</span>,</div>
          <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;available: <span class="ac">true</span> <span class="cm">// ✓</span></div>
          <div>}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-copy reveal d1">
        <div class="section-label">// about</div>
        <h2>Code that<br><em>ships.</em></h2>
        <p>I build full-stack applications that don't just work — they perform. Clean architecture, readable code, and zero tolerance for tech debt. I've shipped products used by hundreds of thousands of users across three continents.</p>
        <p>Whether it's a SaaS MVP in 4 weeks or a performance overhaul of a legacy system, I work fast without cutting corners. My clients don't need to manage me — they just need to give me a clear brief.</p>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag">React</span><span class="tag">Node.js</span><span class="tag">Go</span>
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span><span class="tag">AWS</span><span class="tag">Docker</span><span class="tag">TypeScript</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section id="services" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="section-label reveal">// services</div>
    <h2 class="reveal">What I<br><em>build.</em></h2>
    <div class="svc-list">
      <div class="svc-item reveal"><div class="svc-n">&gt;_ 01</div><div><div class="svc-title">Full Stack Web Apps</div><div class="svc-desc">End-to-end product development — from database schema to deployed frontend. React, Node, Go, PostgreSQL. Scalable from day one.</div></div><div class="svc-tag">Core</div></div>
      <div class="svc-item reveal"><div class="svc-n">&gt;_ 02</div><div><div class="svc-title">API Design & Integration</div><div class="svc-desc">REST and GraphQL APIs built for speed and maintainability. Third-party integrations, webhooks, auth systems — done right the first time.</div></div><div class="svc-tag">Backend</div></div>
      <div class="svc-item reveal"><div class="svc-n">&gt;_ 03</div><div><div class="svc-title">SaaS MVP Development</div><div class="svc-desc">From zero to launched in 4–8 weeks. I scope ruthlessly, ship the core, and iterate. No bloat, no scope creep — just working software.</div></div><div class="svc-tag">Product</div></div>
      <div class="svc-item reveal"><div class="svc-n">&gt;_ 04</div><div><div class="svc-title">Performance Audits & Refactors</div><div class="svc-desc">Slow app? Legacy codebase? I diagnose, fix, and document. Clients typically see 40–80% performance improvements after an audit.</div></div><div class="svc-tag">Optimize</div></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="wrap">
  <section id="process" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="section-label reveal">// process</div>
    <h2 class="reveal">How I<br><em>execute.</em></h2>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="p-step reveal"><div class="p-num">INIT_01</div><div class="p-name">Spec & Scope</div><div class="p-desc">We define the problem clearly before writing a line of code. Detailed spec, tech stack decision, and a fixed timeline. No ambiguity.</div></div>
      <div class="p-step reveal d1"><div class="p-num">BUILD_02</div><div class="p-name">Architecture & Build</div><div class="p-desc">I build in weekly sprints with progress updates. You have visibility into everything — not just the final result.</div></div>
